cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper deals with the problem of 3D reconstruction of objects, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The proposed method uses a deep neural network, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of point cloud data, which is often used in robotics (cs.RO) for tasks such as localization and mapping.
